sequenceDiagram
    participant APP as Application
    participant DEV as Device Driver (ILI2130)
    participant BUS as I2C Bus Driver
    participant MERLIN as Merlin
    participant OS as Camelot-OS + DTS
    participant HW as I2C HW + Peripheral

    APP->>BUS: i2c_driver_probe(label)
    BUS->>MERLIN: merlin_platform_driver_register()
    MERLIN->>OS: Check ownership + resolve DTS metadata
    OS-->>MERLIN: devh, baseaddr, IRQ, GPIO
    MERLIN-->>BUS: Registration OK

    APP->>BUS: i2c_driver_init(speed, mode)
    BUS->>MERLIN: map() + configure_gpio()
    MERLIN->>OS: syscalls for mapping/GPIO
    OS-->>MERLIN: OK
    BUS->>HW: Configure timing + enable controller

    APP->>DEV: ilitech_2130_probe/init()
    DEV->>BUS: i2c_bus_read7()/write7()
    BUS->>MERLIN: merlin_ioread/iowrite + polling helpers
    MERLIN->>HW: MMIO transactions
    HW-->>MERLIN: Status/data
    MERLIN-->>BUS: Transfer result
    BUS-->>DEV: Read/write result
    DEV-->>APP: Device data/status
